  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per day, when the investigator has confirmed a critical hit with a studied strike, he can deal the strike’s maximum damage instead of rolling damage as normal. This includes the damage dealt by the successful attack as well as the additional damage from the studied strike. He can expend a use of inspiration to use this ability a second time per day. Using this ability doesn’t require an action.</p>\n<p>The investigator must have the numerical strike talent and be at least 13th level to select this talent.</p>"
